AI is reshaping markets the way the printing press reshaped information and electronic trading reshaped access.

We’re entering a new era for market architecture, integrity, and collective intelligence.

@Nasdaq President Tal Cohen shares his full reflections from @NVIDIA GTC

@SECGov Nasdaq's equity token design will maintain what defines U.S. equity markets: 

✓ Price discovery ✓ Consolidated liquidity ✓ Investor experience 

A regulated bridge between on-chain records and off-chain identity.
